  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parallel Rift is a four-dimensional puzzle game where you navigate through interconnected spaces along the W-axis to reach the goal. Experience an unseen direction in this casual first-person puzzle adventure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Four Dimensions?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, four-dimensional space is perceived as a three-dimensional cross-section. Players must master both traditional 3D movement and W-axis traversal to overcome seemingly impossible challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Streaming & Content Creation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We welcome all gameplay videos and live streams of this game. Whether you are an individual or a company, monetized or not, feel free to share your experience!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parallel Rift is a four-dimensional puzzle game where you navigate through interconnected spaces along the W-axis to reach the goal. Experience an unseen direction in this casual first-person puzzle adventure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Four Dimensions?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, four-dimensional space is perceived as a three-dimensional cross-section. Players must master both traditional 3D movement and W-axis traversal to overcome seemingly impossible challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Streaming & Content Creation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We welcome all gameplay videos and live streams of this game. Whether you are an individual or a company, monetized or not, feel free to share your experience!</p>",
